text: Expecting Amish is a 2014 drama made for television movie. It was shown on the Lifetime channel. == Story == A 18-year-old girl Hannah Yoder is about to join the church and get married. She decided she likes better the Hollywood life style even it means she will never see her family again. == Actors == * Aj Michalka * Alyson Stoner * Cayden Boyd * Aurelia Scheppers == Other websites == * * * Expecting Amish on Lifetime Category:2014 drama movies Category:Television movies
title: Expecting Amish
